      "prompt": "Convert the input landscape into traditional Chinese gongbi landscape painting style. Preserve mountain shapes, water paths, trees, rocks, buildings if present, depth, and original composition. Use delicate outlines, fine texture strokes, layered ink washes, and elegant mineral color."
